He was surgeon to the Royal Infirmary of Edinburgh for 29 years, during which time he produced the above work. Noted for its clarity and precision it went through seven editions, the last being published in 1801. "Benjamin Bell should be regarded as the first of the Edinburgh scientific surgeons.
